 got news for you people:
Dear Yahoo! Groups Members,

The Yahoo! Groups service will be down Friday March 15 9:00 PM PST (GMT-8) 
as we move our servers to a new facility. We expect the service to be back up the 
morning of Sunday March 17.

During this time the web site will be unavailable and email will not be delivered. 
(Some users may experience email non-delivery notices, but all email should be 
delivered once service has resumed.) Please note: once the service is back up, there 
will be email delays due to backlog. We expect these delays to last no longer than 1 
day. Please do not re-send email to your group as it will only add to delays.

We apologize for any inconvenience this may cause.

The Yahoo! Groups Team
